Package: decampr
Title: Converts the DataCamp Lesson format to Ines Montani's open course format.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ted",
           family = "Laderas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tedladeras@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: "`decampr` consists of some simple utilities to process R-based DataCamp lessons to Ines Montani's Gatsby/Binder based course setup available here: https://github.com/ines/course-starter-r `decampr` speeds up building these courses by parsing the DataCamp format and outputting the correct files (chapter.mds, exercises, solutions, and multiple choice questions)."
